12:59.521 --> 13:01.805
Corporation. I'll see if I can remember that we 
said that. We wanted whatever arrangement we came

13:04.430 --> 13:13.005
up with, we wanted the quality of services to be 
maintained. We wanted the quality of facilities

13:13.025 --> 13:17.814
to be maintained. We felt that an objective would 
be to lower the assessment rate We said that we, the

13:25.525 --> 13:35.754
development corporation, needed to be in control 
of planning and development. And there was one or

13:35.774 --> 13:36.975
two others. And these sound very altruistic, but 
we've been altruistic for 16 years. And we

13:42.580 --> 13:45.162
presented those to the elected directors. And 
they said, gee, that sounds great. We agree with

13:47.184 --> 13:48.005
that. Now, how do we translate that into a plan of 
action? That's what we worked for four years on.

13:53.970 --> 13:55.431
