23:14.985 --> 23:18.030
seats being heavily contested. I see a lot of 
what's going on. in public politics now happening

23:22.057 --> 23:26.803
on the board. And I think that board will make the 
United Times become militant vis-a-vis the

23:26.863 --> 23:33.711
Development Corporation. So you see that as a 
divisive, or potentially divisive? Could be,

23:39.998 --> 23:42.902
yeah. Now, we have tried to be responsive. We sit 
down with whatever community group has a problem.

23:50.710 --> 23:53.815
I can't tell you the hours we put into that. Not only 
myself, that's my job, but all the executives in

23:54.215 --> 23:59.263
this company. If there's somebody in the 
