25:44.616 --> 25:46.218
newspapers all the time. And, you know, we'd have 
lunch, and he'd say, you know, I hate to do this to

25:47.240 --> 25:52.250
you because I like you. I said, I'm running for 
Congress. So that's not going to end. No, that's

25:56.557 --> 25:57.559
going to increase. I think it's going to increase. 
I think we're going to see that kind of dynamic

25:58.701 --> 26:02.769
happening. So you've got a job there. What about, 
speaking of tensions, I don't know if this is a good

26:07.263 --> 26:10.847
time. Do you want to take a break or something? 
